data.description: Wow! 5 BR/3BA pool home in amenity-rich Bartram Springs! The home has a private outdoor area with large custom pool, heated spa, pergola, kitchen and sun deck. Recent updates include new roof (2022), 4 ton a/c compressor (2023), new kitchen cabinets and countertops, new double front door with plantation shutters, new dishwasher and microwave (2022) and water heater.  Features include wood floors, open floor plan, plantation shutters and close proximity to the highly-rated Bartram Springs Elementary School. The large glass-enclosed back porch is not included in the listed square footage (not under air), but provides extra living space for much of the year. If you aren't familiar with the amenities in this established neighborhood, be sure to look at the photos in the listing.
